{"title":"Pogo-很喜欢的音乐分享","uid":"785e931b8375c9e7032f41e0ac8d47a2","slug":"Pogo-最近很喜欢的音乐分享","date":"2022-10-23T09:53:55.000Z","updated":"2022-10-23T12:08:48.178Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Pogo-最近很喜欢的音乐分享.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/随笔配图/206ad3cac8878c9ee58e4d371a504e44ea05941e.31g1xdu88og0.png","content":"<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Pogo是一个新的电子音乐艺术家，来自佩思、澳大利亚。他因为记录一些小的电影里的声音出名，把那些声音重新变成新的音乐。 Pogo的许多作品几乎全部由他采样的声音组成。</p></blockquote>\n<p>对于<strong>Pogo</strong>，我只能想到<strong>fantasy</strong>这个词。作者大多通过剪辑电影片段+Remix的方式来进行创作，创意和调音都很惊艳。作者原创首发都是在Youtube上，b站上有网友搬运来的视频。很久没有这种发掘到宝藏的感觉了，上一个感到这么惊艳的是看到sakana（都很低产）。</p>\n<p>Pogo的Youtube主页，喜欢可以订阅：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/Fagottron\">Pogo主页</a> 。分享三首我比较喜欢的作品：</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Boy &amp; Bear</strong> - 剪辑自《小熊维尼》</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=\"330\" height=\"86\" src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=522511545&auto=0&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 30% 45%;\">\n<iframe style=\"position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; top: 0;\" src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=13563764&bvid=BV1Cx411J75J&cid=22200482&page=1&high_quality=1&danmaku=0\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Forget</strong> - 混剪自有年头的迪士尼动画《小公主》《花木兰》等</p>\n<p>很好的作品，可惜在国内稍有些热度居然是因为一些抖音低创…</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=\"330\" height=\"86\" src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=35804572&auto=0&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 30% 45%;\">\n<iframe style=\"position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; top: 0;\" src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=10773582&bvid=BV17x411Y7nx&cid=17776270&page=1&danmaku=0\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Data &amp; Picard</strong> - 剪辑自《星际迷航》</p>\n<p>歌词也剪得很好，弹幕里有克林贡语翻译</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=\"330\" height=\"86\" src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=451376031&auto=0&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 30% 45%;\">\n<iframe style=\"position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; top: 0;\" src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=23258902&bvid=BV1FW411F7bN&cid=38731410&page=1&high_quality=1&danmaku=1\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div>","feature":true,"text":" Pogo是一个新的电子音乐艺术家，来自佩思、澳大利亚。他因为记录一些小的电影里的声音出名，把那些声音重新变成新的音乐。 Pogo的许多作品几乎全部由他采样的声音组成。 对于Pogo，我只能想到fantasy这个词。作者大多通过剪辑电影片段+Remix的方式来进行创作，创意和调音...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":429,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"日常随笔","slug":"日常随笔","count":1,"path":"api/categories/日常随笔.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"日常随笔","slug":"日常随笔","count":1,"path":"api/tags/日常随笔.json"},{"name":"音乐","slug":"音乐","count":1,"path":"api/tags/音乐.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"月下叶子","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/about/博客头像.1rm6v48dfu1s.jpg","link":"/","description":"日月东升西落，未曾负你我","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/moonlightleaf","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/leaf_in_the_moon","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"C++内存管理机制by侯捷","uid":"c81f05bf413cc3f19b34e5ac7f84ab62","slug":"C++内存管理机制by侯捷","date":"2022-10-16T07:54:28.000Z","updated":"2022-10-18T07:45:52.996Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/C++内存管理机制by侯捷.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/C++内存管理机制/View.1wlouym8jmn4.jpg","text":"《 C++内存管理机制 》by侯捷-一文总结(持续更新) 目录 1. Overview 2. C++ Memory Primitives 3. 四个层面的基本用法 4-6. new&#x2F;delete expression 7. array new，array delete ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C++内存管理机制","slug":"C-内存管理机制","count":1,"path":"api/categories/C-内存管理机制.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"C++内存管理机制","slug":"C-内存管理机制","count":1,"path":"api/tags/C-内存管理机制.json"}],"author":{"name":"月下叶子","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@ma